---
title: Zesty Honey-Glazed Beef Rump & Garlic Veg with Almonds & Chilli Flakes
description: Fresh, fast, and oh-so-flavourful! Tonight, juicy beef meets a zesty glaze of lemon, honey and oregano. Add some vibrant greens, topped off with a kick of chilli and the perfect crunch of almonds. Healthy never tasted so delicious!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
